1
00:00:04,437 --> 00:00:07,674
Veliki umovi
pricaju o idejama.

2
00:00:07,674 --> 00:00:10,510
Prosecni umovi o stvariama.

3
00:00:10,510 --> 00:00:13,847
osrednji umovi
pricaju o ljudima.

4
00:00:13,847 --> 00:00:18,752
narode, ostavicu vas uz
ovu misao ali vraticu se

5
00:00:18,752 --> 00:00:23,423
kasnije veceras, moram
i ja od necega da zivim.

6
00:00:23,423 --> 00:00:26,960
Voleo bih da je
svako vece subota vece

7
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,723
i svaki dan nedelja.

8
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:45,970
lsuse, josife i marijo!

9
00:00:55,422 --> 00:01:01,019
u redu, onda ajde
da te nahranimo.

10
00:01:07,434 --> 00:01:08,025
33 godine kasnije.

11
00:01:08,568 --> 00:01:14,473
nemoj da places.
ti imas veliki dar.

12
00:01:15,842 --> 00:01:17,969
Vama je ovo dar?

13
00:01:21,781 --> 00:01:24,484
Vidim da nisi spremna
da budes majka.

14
00:01:24,484 --> 00:01:27,087
- mislila sam da se
ovo meni nece desiti.

15
00:01:27,087 --> 00:01:31,751
opusti se i udahni duboko.

16
00:01:34,761 --> 00:01:36,830
o boze, sta da radim?

17
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:39,766
da li hoces da
ragovaras sa nekim?

18
00:01:39,766 --> 00:01:42,599
Videcu da li ima vremena.

19
00:01:45,038 --> 00:01:45,936
megi!

20
00:01:51,010 --> 00:01:53,843
slusaj, imam nesto
sto bi te zanimalo.

21
00:01:55,482 --> 00:01:57,550
nije nevina, ali
je nesto najblize

22
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:59,385
tome na sta sam
ikada naletela.

23
00:01:59,385 --> 00:02:02,122
ovde u dosijeu imamo devojku

24
00:02:02,122 --> 00:02:04,657
od 23 godine megi tejt.

25
00:02:04,657 --> 00:02:07,727
njeni bioloski
roditelji su mrtvi.

26
00:02:07,727 --> 00:02:10,930
odrasla je u
prihvatilistvu do silovanja

27
00:02:10,930 --> 00:02:12,799
kada je imala 14 godina.

28
00:02:12,799 --> 00:02:15,435
Posle par pokusaja

29
00:02:15,435 --> 00:02:18,905
operacije utrobe zivela je

30
00:02:18,905 --> 00:02:24,911
uglavnom ubolnici. bilo
je dosta komplikacija.

31
00:02:24,911 --> 00:02:30,750
jajnici koji su joj narusili
zdravlje su izvadeni,

32
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:36,055
nakon cega,uz hormonske
terapije, postaje bolje.

33
00:02:36,055 --> 00:02:39,926
sto nas dovodi do sledeceg.

34
00:02:39,926 --> 00:02:43,830
sedam godina
kasnije tvrdi da je u

35
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:47,767
monogamnoj vezi
sa, pa sad slusajte.

36
00:02:47,767 --> 00:02:50,803
sterilnim covekom.

37
00:02:50,803 --> 00:02:53,806
neverovatno, zar ne?

38
00:02:53,806 --> 00:02:55,108
tvrdi da je tako?

39
00:02:55,108 --> 00:02:58,407
- Pa jos moramo da
potvrdimo ovo stanje.

40
00:02:58,478 --> 00:03:01,614
nadam se da zante jos.
- Pa nema stigmate

41
00:03:01,614 --> 00:03:03,550
niti ista tako, ali ima...

42
00:03:03,550 --> 00:03:05,818
jedna slucajnost uz ovaj

43
00:03:05,818 --> 00:03:07,720
medicinski fenomen.

44
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,889
da li mi se to cini da je
nesto hitno u pitanju?

45
00:03:09,889 --> 00:03:11,891
tu ste u pravu.

46
00:03:11,891 --> 00:03:16,829
Vldite. cudo ili ne...

47
00:03:16,829 --> 00:03:19,699
milsim da ona hoce da prekine
trudnocu.

48
00:03:19,699 --> 00:03:22,068
a koja je to slucajnost?

49
00:03:22,068 --> 00:03:26,129
Pa ovo dete bi se rodilo
pred kraj decembra.

50
00:03:30,543 --> 00:03:32,545
e, pa gde si ti?

51
00:03:32,545 --> 00:03:34,035
gladan sam.

52
00:03:35,615 --> 00:03:40,053
dame i gospodo, treba
da ispravimo put.

53
00:03:40,053 --> 00:03:45,658
ko zeli?
- ja cu.

54
00:03:45,658 --> 00:03:47,694
odlicno.

55
00:03:47,694 --> 00:03:49,855
tvoja je.

56
00:03:52,131 --> 00:03:54,934
sta se zbiva, sto cutis?

57
00:03:54,934 --> 00:03:58,504
- nesto sam
htela da ti kazem.

58
00:03:58,504 --> 00:04:00,699
sta to?

59
00:04:07,747 --> 00:04:08,873
trudna sam.

60
00:04:11,985 --> 00:04:14,654
sta rece?
- kazem trudna sam,

61
00:04:14,654 --> 00:04:17,145
ne pitaj kako
jednostavno jesam.

62
00:04:18,791 --> 00:04:22,962
nisam u fazonu da me neko zeza.

63
00:04:22,962 --> 00:04:26,693
ne zezam.

64
00:04:30,136 --> 00:04:33,139
nema smisla.

65
00:04:33,139 --> 00:04:35,675
o cemu ti pricas!?

66
00:04:35,675 --> 00:04:39,712
sta kazes, trudna si?

67
00:04:39,712 --> 00:04:43,082
s kim se jebes?
- ni sa kim.

68
00:04:43,082 --> 00:04:47,610
jel onbaj debeli bert?

69
00:04:50,757 --> 00:04:52,659
a? - ne.

70
00:04:52,659 --> 00:04:56,095
Pa zanmo da nije moje, zar ne?

71
00:04:56,095 --> 00:04:57,289
ne znam..

72
00:04:57,530 --> 00:04:58,963
- zar ne?
- ne.

73
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:01,764
sranje!

74
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:05,096
ti si jebena kurva!

75
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:58,817
hoces da razgovaramo?

76
00:06:28,654 --> 00:06:30,178
kako se ovo dogodilo?

77
00:06:34,293 --> 00:06:36,362
neko cudo prirode.

78
00:06:36,362 --> 00:06:38,197
jesi bila kod lekara?

79
00:06:38,197 --> 00:06:43,302
da, kaze da je to
boziji dar, jel mozes

80
00:06:43,302 --> 00:06:47,238
da verujes? -mozda
je pogresila.

81
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:51,304
nije greska.

82
00:06:54,447 --> 00:06:57,417
samo znam da se desilo.

83
00:06:57,417 --> 00:07:00,682
nije trebalo, ali jeste.

84
00:07:01,988 --> 00:07:05,291
l kunem ti se...

85
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:10,730
da nemam drugoga. jel mi verujes?

86
00:07:10,730 --> 00:07:16,225
zasto bih?
- zato sto je istina.

87
00:07:23,009 --> 00:07:24,444
Verujem ti.

88
00:07:24,444 --> 00:07:29,108
ok? Verujem ti.

89
00:07:30,783 --> 00:07:32,885
sta cemo sad?

90
00:07:32,885 --> 00:07:36,218
ste cemo sa ovim sranjem?

91
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:40,059
nemozemo da spavamo.

92
00:07:40,059 --> 00:07:44,464
mislim, moramo
nesto da smislimo.

93
00:07:44,464 --> 00:07:47,467
Pa mozemo i ujutru. - ne.

94
00:07:47,467 --> 00:07:52,404
ne, moramo sad da smislimo
sta cemo.

95
00:07:57,944 --> 00:08:00,513
kako cemo to sada?

96
00:08:00,513 --> 00:08:05,883
ne mozemo da
priustimo dete. -znam.

97
00:08:06,919 --> 00:08:08,352
znam.

98
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,352
sta cemo da radimo?

99
00:08:23,769 --> 00:08:25,168
abortiracu.

100
00:08:30,009 --> 00:08:32,170
jel mogu sad da spavam?

101
00:09:06,212 --> 00:09:08,806
Vanda.

102
00:09:09,782 --> 00:09:13,115
Vracam se odmah...

103
00:09:20,359 --> 00:09:23,029
uspori malo, lsuse, megi!

104
00:09:23,029 --> 00:09:26,365
dodi, sta je...
lzgledas grozno.

105
00:09:26,365 --> 00:09:28,265
treba mi jos kesa.

106
00:09:28,334 --> 00:09:32,438
o boze!

107
00:09:32,438 --> 00:09:35,805
mislio je da ga varam.

108
00:09:38,911 --> 00:09:41,480
odjebi ga.

109
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:44,540
treba da ga sutnes sad.

110
00:09:46,218 --> 00:09:47,853
uzmite sami, hvala.

111
00:09:47,853 --> 00:09:51,186
da, aha, samo malo...

112
00:09:53,092 --> 00:09:54,527
dodi ovamo, trebas mi.

113
00:09:54,527 --> 00:09:56,017
ma ovatis me bart!

114
00:10:00,533 --> 00:10:03,102
kad prode spic za rucek,

115
00:10:03,102 --> 00:10:05,972
da dodes u moju kancelariju!

116
00:10:05,972 --> 00:10:08,406
ali ti nemas kancelariju!

117
00:10:08,474 --> 00:10:09,408
Problemi sa osobljem.

118
00:10:09,408 --> 00:10:10,500
mozes da zivis kod mene

119
00:10:10,576 --> 00:10:12,311
koliko god zelis, znas to.

120
00:10:12,311 --> 00:10:16,282
da, znam, ali...

121
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:17,650
Pomirili smo se.

122
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:19,413
bice sve u redu.

123
00:10:21,387 --> 00:10:23,089
Pa kad ces da...

124
00:10:23,089 --> 00:10:25,257
ldem za dve nedelje.

125
00:10:25,257 --> 00:10:27,360
znaci za dve nedelje

126
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:30,158
sve ce biti bolje. Po starom.

127
00:10:32,898 --> 00:10:34,490
mogu da te otpustim.

128
00:10:39,071 --> 00:10:40,936
dolazim tatice!

129
00:10:47,346 --> 00:10:49,211
jel verujete u boga?

130
00:10:52,184 --> 00:10:56,314
da. - Pa zasto
niste u crkvi onda?

131
00:10:58,424 --> 00:11:00,619
neko mora i da radi.

132
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:06,257
a vi?

133
00:11:08,934 --> 00:11:12,138
ne daj da te takvi ljudi smore.

134
00:11:12,138 --> 00:11:13,298
malo me je zatekla, Vanda.

135
00:11:14,473 --> 00:11:19,111
Vidis, bas to i zele.
da ti udu u glavu.

136
00:11:19,111 --> 00:11:21,238
Pa uspelo je, osecam krivicu.

137
00:11:22,281 --> 00:11:26,911
Pa ofarbaj se u palvo.

138
00:11:30,322 --> 00:11:33,092
slusaj, hvala ti za danas.

139
00:11:33,092 --> 00:11:35,322
- Volim te draga.
- cao.

140
00:11:49,575 --> 00:11:51,304
trudna? uplasena?

141
00:12:19,705 --> 00:12:21,605
sta je bilo?

142
00:12:22,274 --> 00:12:24,076
sta je bilo?
- zar nisi cuo?

143
00:12:24,076 --> 00:12:25,043
ne, sta je bilo?

144
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:33,044
halo? - bog vas
posmatra gresnici.

145
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,714
znas sta...

146
00:12:41,694 --> 00:12:47,655
duso, to su neka
deca, ajde.

147
00:12:52,671 --> 00:12:55,231
u redu je, ok?

148
00:12:58,244 --> 00:13:03,045
bilo je grozno. - znam, ne brini.

149
00:13:05,618 --> 00:13:07,279
spavaj.

150
00:13:08,788 --> 00:13:11,518
bice sve u redu.

151
00:13:26,372 --> 00:13:27,807
fetus je dete.

152
00:13:27,807 --> 00:13:31,243
- lzaberi zivot za
zivot sa ponosom.

153
00:13:31,243 --> 00:13:32,403
ubice beba.

154
00:13:40,452 --> 00:13:43,546
ne morate to da
radite. mozete odustati...

155
00:13:52,164 --> 00:13:54,394
abortus nije kontrola radanja!

156
00:14:03,309 --> 00:14:07,446
sta treb ada
uradimo da je prime?

157
00:14:07,446 --> 00:14:11,684
- gospodine popunite
formulare tamo.

158
00:14:11,684 --> 00:14:14,320
za koliko mogu da je prime?

159
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:17,312
kao sto rekoh, popunite formulare
i doci ce po nju.

160
00:14:18,591 --> 00:14:20,759
ovo je besmisleno,
samo da znate!

161
00:14:20,759 --> 00:14:23,195
- lzvinite, nama
je tako svaki dan.

162
00:14:23,195 --> 00:14:24,184
e pa nama nije!

163
00:15:10,376 --> 00:15:12,207
megi t?

164
00:16:22,014 --> 00:16:23,504
oblaci se!

165
00:16:34,860 --> 00:16:36,929
Podmetanje eksploziva

166
00:16:36,929 --> 00:16:39,264
u zdravstvene ustanove je

167
00:16:39,264 --> 00:16:41,000
sekundarni terorizam,

168
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:43,468
da bi se sprecilo spasasavanje.

169
00:16:45,704 --> 00:16:46,872
ne razumem.

170
00:16:46,872 --> 00:16:50,672
kako mogu da se
nazivaju za zivot?

171
00:16:56,882 --> 00:17:00,652
to je kao onaj
ludak u oklahomi...

172
00:17:00,652 --> 00:17:02,677
on misli da je junak.

173
00:17:11,397 --> 00:17:15,334
sta znamo o ovom liku?
- neka skitnica.

174
00:17:15,334 --> 00:17:19,464
jel moze da se kupi?
- to mi treba da saznamo.

175
00:17:43,362 --> 00:17:46,297
zovem da proverim kada
mogu da zakazem.

176
00:17:50,402 --> 00:17:55,635
a koliko ce to da traje?
Pa da se javim kasnije...?

177
00:17:56,809 --> 00:18:01,439
ok, ne. hvala vam.

178
00:18:04,983 --> 00:18:06,644
kako je bilo?

179
00:18:07,619 --> 00:18:08,711
sranje.

180
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:16,395
ali naleteo sam
na tipa ispred radnje.

181
00:18:16,395 --> 00:18:18,564
setio nas se sa klinike.

182
00:18:18,564 --> 00:18:21,733
stvarno? -da, kaze da

183
00:18:21,733 --> 00:18:25,003
zna kako mozemo da zaradimo.

184
00:18:25,003 --> 00:18:29,108
- ne, necemo te prevare.
- slusaj...

185
00:18:29,108 --> 00:18:33,712
bio je u agenciji za
usvajanje i pricao mi je

186
00:18:33,712 --> 00:18:38,117
o nekom paru koji dugo
pokusava da usvoji dete.

187
00:18:38,117 --> 00:18:43,789
ali nisu uspeli. l
sada su spremni da plate

188
00:18:43,789 --> 00:18:46,091
50 hiljada dolara...

189
00:18:46,091 --> 00:18:49,428
da dobiju nase dete.
- zaboravi. -zasto?

190
00:18:49,428 --> 00:18:51,797
- zar stvarno
moras da pitas to?

191
00:18:51,797 --> 00:18:53,866
ljudi to stalno rade.

192
00:18:53,866 --> 00:18:58,428
jedina razlika je sto
zaobilazimo birokratiju.

193
00:19:00,672 --> 00:19:03,903
ovo nam je sansa da se
izvadimo iz dugova.

194
00:19:05,744 --> 00:19:09,441
megi, mozemo
da pocnemo novi zivot.

195
00:19:10,616 --> 00:19:12,050
modemo da odemo.

196
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:16,510
ja bih da odem odavde,
a sigurno i ti.

197
00:19:20,692 --> 00:19:24,830
ok, recimi jos jednom...

198
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:28,534
zasto ne mogu usvoje?

199
00:19:28,534 --> 00:19:33,472
nije da nisu probali...
na mnogim su listama. ali,

200
00:19:33,472 --> 00:19:35,174
stalno ih zaobilaze.

201
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:38,877
kako to. ako su tako dobri,

202
00:19:38,877 --> 00:19:41,213
zasto ih odbijaju?

203
00:19:41,213 --> 00:19:44,183
ne znam. zbog
birokratije, politike.

204
00:19:44,183 --> 00:19:48,086
l ako ne poznajete ljude
iz agencije, nema sanse.

205
00:19:48,086 --> 00:19:51,578
jel mogu opet da vidim sliku?
- naravno.

206
00:19:58,697 --> 00:20:00,933
kako to da nemaju decu?

207
00:20:00,933 --> 00:20:06,638
- Pa, nasli su tacku na njenoj
materici i to je bio rak.

208
00:20:06,638 --> 00:20:08,807
Pa su morali da je operisu.

209
00:20:08,807 --> 00:20:11,109
to je bilo prve godine braka.

210
00:20:11,109 --> 00:20:13,168
lmala je 21 godinu.

211
00:20:15,948 --> 00:20:18,784
ne znam kako da vam kazem...

212
00:20:18,784 --> 00:20:20,919
to je ponuda i potraznja.

213
00:20:20,919 --> 00:20:22,588
ljednostavno nema

214
00:20:22,588 --> 00:20:26,091
dovoljno belih beba.
zato mnogi moraju da idu

215
00:20:26,091 --> 00:20:28,527
u inostranstvo na razna mesta.

216
00:20:28,527 --> 00:20:30,462
drugi cekaju pravu stvar

217
00:20:30,462 --> 00:20:32,623
kad ne dode oni su ocajni...

218
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:38,627
zato ovaj par hoce
da da puno para.

219
00:20:38,971 --> 00:20:42,007
zar to nije nelegalno?
- ne nije...

220
00:20:42,007 --> 00:20:44,042
ti imas pravo na svoje dete.

221
00:20:44,042 --> 00:20:46,745
l moze da ga usvoji
svako kome dozvolis.

222
00:20:46,745 --> 00:20:47,980
mozda zaobilazimo

223
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:49,880
par tehnickih
pitanja. ali to je to.

224
00:20:52,718 --> 00:20:55,220
lzvinite ako
sam nepristojna,

225
00:20:55,220 --> 00:20:57,814
ali... sta vi imate od toga?

226
00:21:00,492 --> 00:21:02,628
slusaj, pitanje je dobro i ne
smeta mi da odgovorim.

227
00:21:02,628 --> 00:21:05,564
ja dobijam honorar
za pronalazenje

228
00:21:05,564 --> 00:21:07,099
i to je 10000 dolara.

229
00:21:07,099 --> 00:21:11,092
jel to... - ali se ne kosi
sa vasom isplatom.

230
00:21:11,903 --> 00:21:14,172
slusaj, ja nisam svetac.

231
00:21:14,172 --> 00:21:18,802
ali hocu da uradim nesto
dobro. ali bih i u raj.

232
00:21:20,178 --> 00:21:24,049
a verujem da je
ovo dobra stvar.

233
00:21:24,049 --> 00:21:27,519
l mislim da i ti u to verujes.

234
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:29,885
sad moram da idem
a vi razmislite.

235
00:21:31,089 --> 00:21:33,158
jel mogu da zadrzim ovu sliku?

236
00:21:33,158 --> 00:21:36,695
moram da se pridrzavam
nekih pravila...

237
00:21:36,695 --> 00:21:39,231
ali ako ste za ovo,

238
00:21:39,231 --> 00:21:41,566
mogu da sredim
da upoznate ljude.

239
00:21:41,566 --> 00:21:42,931
Pre nego
sto se porodite.

240
00:21:48,173 --> 00:21:50,275
jos jednom hvala
sto ste dosli.

241
00:21:50,275 --> 00:21:52,110
